Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:25.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}月影照らす帰り道　公園を通り過ぎると
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:32.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}規則正しく揺れるブランコに思わず未来を重ねる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:39.52,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}ゆうべの雨を吸い込んだ砂に足跡を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:46.63,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}ココに居ることを確かめるたび少し泣きそうになる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:52.95,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}ループするイメージを抜け出して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:22:00.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}最後にはヒトツだときみが言う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:07.51,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}ぼくが創った世界には色や匂いが足りなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:14.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}届きそうな明日さえも描けなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:21.94,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}きみの匂いに誘われて触れた色に目を奪われた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:26.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}足りないものはココにあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:47.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}宇宙のヒミツに触れたら弾けたきみの夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:53.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}ほらねと得意気な顔できみは笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:00.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\be5}4月の風が吹いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:07.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\be5}3月のぼくを乗せて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:20.17,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}5月のぼくの方へブランコを揺らして未来へ通り抜ける
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------EDCN-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:25.30,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}月光照亮的归途中　当穿过公园时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:32.32,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}不由得将未来与平稳摇摆的秋千重叠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:39.52,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}足迹留在了沾满昨晚雨水的沙子上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:46.63,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}每次确认自己的存在都会有股泪水涌上心头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:52.95,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}抛开那循环着的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:22:00.68,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}最后只想告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:07.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}我所创造的世界还缺少色彩与味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:14.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}就算是触手可及的明天也无法描绘出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:21.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}被你的味道所引诱　被触及的色彩迷住了双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.35,0:22:26.29,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}那些欠缺的东西都在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.23,0:22:47.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}梦见了触及宇宙的秘密而兴奋的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:53.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}你满脸得意地笑着向我炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:23:00.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\be5}四月的风吹拂着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:07.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)}{\be5}再乘上三月的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:20.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be5}穿过像秋千一样摇摆不停的未来到五月的我身边去
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  上个月的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个月也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  你拿到多少呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太  太感谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话是这么说  毕竟老板娘那么抠门  应该没那么多…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你住在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是把房租啊饭费什么的扣掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两万元…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.60,0:02:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我自己家里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是做饭又是洗衣服又是打扫卫生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只有八千元…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八千元…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能拿年龄乘以500的钱…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上学前把这里打扫得干干净净的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  垃圾旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  垃圾旅馆的佣工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人来了  欢迎词是欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.22,0:03:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是服务业基本中的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一清早就过来  真是辛苦你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此  刚刚还教育了你们的佣工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的也是要收咨询费的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉…想把那个人一起扫除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈  客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是营业顾问  川尻崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  别人都来和您打招呼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我身体不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  昨天不还很精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  崇子小姐  等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正忙着准备早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨的整理还…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  这可是事关喜翠庄未来的议题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  川尻小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如刚才所介绍的那样 我是担任营业顾问的川尻崇子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来让喜翠庄改头换面的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等您好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人经常来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概每个月来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  作为最根本的改善措施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天所要提出的意见是关于这个旅馆的服务员的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房  回到岗位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好滑头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月是我们来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:05:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  今天的计划是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  要让服务员的着装焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着墨守成规的服务员制服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄不管怎样都免不了一股陈旧之风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用最时尚的潮流来改善这个旅馆的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让客人的满足度也一并提升的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口口相传的长尾效应也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到啊办不到办不到办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这种会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似没一家旅馆的服务员是穿这种的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的陈旧观念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Standing pools gather filth」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一潭死水里就只会滋生出垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们懂不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这陈腐旅馆中凝固一般的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似  被子真的有股陈腐的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Venture
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Nothing venture, nothing win!」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有挑战的话  胜利就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑战…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这种挑战貌似也…不错吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊  不错不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才没看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  工作了工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}小菜这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}诶  是不是有些太暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}才没这回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够靓丽的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺好吗  很合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的会成为挑战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. It's challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明不想挑战的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的  就差个适合这种潮流的客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  说到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得预定今早光临的客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立花先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十多岁的男性  三人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说曹操曹操到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧  小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他吓了一跳…不对  他在感动？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说不定是成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得…立花先生的一行三人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  请让我来拿行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.93,0:08:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  真的不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是饱了你的眼福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的实在是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的挑战失败了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才说不要了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜  额头好红哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  别再说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因为选错了衣服么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更大胆一些才好么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  到底是哪里出错了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COSPLAY？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  果然在生意不怎么样的旅馆里有着各种各样的试验呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生意不怎么样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我很感动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力！  根性！  差不多这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉很让人神往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份努力得不到回报  这才是最大的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃  只要努力下去一定会得到回报的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话怎么讲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…就比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把旗袍的开气再开得高一些之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑战并不是说全都能收到回报的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是迟到会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.29,0:10:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你铁定挨骂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不至于那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说在这个时间回来应该不会挨骂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房难道不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民好像想从头掌握准备晚餐的整个步骤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不需要我做顾问的话  我也不需要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人说不需要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等一下  崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像很消沉的样子  是不是跟他搭句话比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我这就开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子好敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业于大学经管系  还在读硕士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个做顾问的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷在大学时认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白少爷很着急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们旅馆的经营状况非常不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没什么客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  所以才需要挑战呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那个打扮真是讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜喜欢别的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这也不是我们该担心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种打扮不管怎么说还是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢  我想干什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为被老板娘斥责了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说巴小姐和小菜也很不情愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都这么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也知道这有些勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也是为这个旅馆着想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…老妈却…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算失败了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也比什么都不做要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天事情会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皋月姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐总是在我失落的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你刚才那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种毫无根据的鼓励吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  毫无根据的鼓励
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是差劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是  你的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了喜翠庄有没有什么事是我能做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小民也来一起COSPLAY吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意义不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定出乎意外的受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少彻先生会高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好不说「去死」了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要找到…我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是拿了这两万块钱也高兴不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早就过来  还以为你有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那个莫名其妙的女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们也都清楚少爷的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果什么都不做看着旅馆倒闭的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会扯到倒闭的事情上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是些小事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我觉得有点新的改变是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的是指什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把旗袍的开气再开高一点什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但这里要是倒闭的话我就没地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再说倒闭就赶你走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就「萧条」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就很萧条了不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和老板娘正处于激烈争吵中…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.62,0:16:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生意一直都不怎么好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘她也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…既然明白的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多做一些尝试也没什么不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说少爷所做的的确有点歪门邪道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.74,0:17:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还有这样的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件好雅致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说这些都是老板娘做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有的已经有些陈旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全没有破损
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是豆丁老爷在打理的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花的也很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  真是可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个  这打扮是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正门的扫除完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.12,0:18:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好柔软  妈妈你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得这是我第一次在喜翠庄住宿的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘穿的那件哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是你出生的很早以前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时真的很漂亮哦  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然拿出这么让人怀念的东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里  怎么会惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服不就是你设计出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得好像是要什么「新的改变」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后您先生就发火了  没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  已经是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没到遗忘的年纪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎下次光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄也是历史悠久的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  历史悠久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才怎么鞠的躬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在鸡啄米么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样鞠躬对客人十分失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘  我有事要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教训还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之你先听一下啊  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.50,0:20:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘  这次我想的绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能因为早上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天客人增加就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现实也许没有那么天真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  下次一定能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次有更棒的主意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定会有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这喜翠庄来说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是有所改变才对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.55,0:21:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是保留原样才对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想要做到些什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样稍稍考虑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.18,0:23:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}这样还有工作下去的意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我考虑了下是不是要回老家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.82,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我的女服务员人生就此结束了！
